This paper discusses the rise of ransomware and its impact on victims, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also discusses preventative measures, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and cybercrime (cs.CY). The use of machine learning or other AI techniques to detect and prevent ransomware attacks could also be a potential topic, placing the paper in the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper may also discuss data analysis and statistics related to ransomware attacks, which could place it in the category of data science (cs.DS).
